OL,3,CWhy there's ceasefire hopes despite
OL,4,Cfears of a new Gaza offensive
OL,6,FThe morning after, it is now clear
OL,7,Fthat none of those dramatic events
OL,8,Fwere as consequential as they appeared
OL,9,Fat first sight.
OL,11,FIn Cairo, Doha, and Washington DC -
OL,12,Fthe key capitals through which
OL,13,Fnegotiations are being mediated and
OL,14,Finfluenced - the biggest optimists
OL,15,Frevealed an enthusiasm from both sides
OL,16,Fto gain leverage and to wrong-foot
OL,17,Ftheir opponents.
