OL,3,CWhy there's ceasefire hopes despite
OL,4,Cfears of a new Gaza offensive
OL,6,FBut that, in turn, suggests they are
OL,7,Fstill trying to shape conditions for a
OL,8,Fdeal this week, according to three
OL,9,Fdiplomatic sources with sight on the
OL,10,Fnegotiations.
OL,12,FFirst came an evacuation order issued
OL,13,Fto 100,000 people in eastern Rafah on
OL,14,FMonday morning, which appeared to
OL,15,Fsignal the start of in the southern
OL,16,FGazan city.
OL,18,FThe attack could have devastating
OL,19,Fhumanitarian consequences and threaten
OL,20,Fto end hopes for peace, according to
OL,21,Fthe United Nations.
