OL,3,CWhy there's ceasefire hopes despite
OL,4,Cfears of a new Gaza offensive
OL,6,FAnd, the CIA chief William Burns is
OL,7,Fstill in the region to apply pressure.
OL,9,FA foreign diplomatic source tells ITV
OL,10,FNews that these are conditions for
OL,11,Fprogress: "We are fed up, but still
OL,12,Fhopeful".
